shortDescription: George’s Modern Relaxed Fit Jeans for men are a wardrobe essential. These premium comfort jeans provide the right amount of stretch and are machine washable for easy care. These men’s jeans are designed to sit at the waist, relaxed through the hip and thigh with a straight leg. These jeans are available in assorted colors and sizes. Pair with a tee or a button-up for a classic look. George is a one-stop range for men who want to look good effortlessly, and brings timeless, masculine looks updated with modern styling and premium design. Only at Walmart.
